    },
    {
      "start": 821.48,
      "end": 821.76,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 822.14,
      "end": 828.26,
      "text": "On the day before our first game, I found out that my mother was very sick."
    },
    {
      "start": 828.26,
      "end": 833.16,
      "text": "So, I quit the team, you know, just started to take care of her."
    },
    {
      "start": 833.16,
      "end": 835.28,
      "text": "Yeah, you know, oh my god."
    },
    {
      "start": 835.72,
      "end": 840.08,
      "text": "You know, I never, I never did perform."
    },
    {
      "start": 841.74,
      "end": 845.27,
      "text": "Now, that's maybe you should give it another shot."
    },
    {
      "start": 845.77,
      "end": 848.15,
      "text": "Yeah, maybe the Dallas Cowgirls have an opening, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 849.34,
      "end": 857.6,
      "text": "네, 오늘은 우리의 마음에 뭔가 독려해주는, 꿈을 장려해주는 그런 메시지로 가득한 내용이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 857.82,
      "end": 859.0,
      "text": "Let's follow our dreams."
    },
    {
      "start": 859.18,
      "end": 860.08,
      "text": "Never too late."
    },
    {
      "start": 860.08,
      "end": 863.26,
      "text": "Yeah, 오늘 이렇게 가슴 속에 담아보시고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 863.72,
      "end": 865.08,
      "text": "우리는 see you tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "start": 865.46,
      "end": 866.44,
      "text": "Have a lovely day."
    },
    {
      "start": 866.52,
      "end": 867.16,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "start": 867.6,
      "end": 869.38,
      "text": "노래 한 곡 들어볼게요."
    }
  ]
}